h3. Steps to Reproduce
 # Create three new releases;
 # Set one as released, one as released *and* archived, leave one as unreleased;
 # Run the following JQL;
{code:java}
Project in ("[name]") and fixVersion in releasedVersions(){code}

h3. Expected Results

Only what is released and not archived should be displayed.
h3. Actual Results

Both the released version and archived released version will be displayed;
h3. Notes

There isn't a native way to filter for archived versions. JRASERVER-66325 suggests implementing a check for {{archivedVersions()}}
